# Optional: Giphy API for in-app GIF search (https://developers.giphy.com/).
# Easiest setup: copy server/giphy-api-key.txt.example to giphy-api-key.txt and paste your key (one line).
# Or set on the server process only — never in the web client or Vite env:
# GIPHY_API_KEY=your_key_here
# BAHUCKEL_GIPHY_API_KEY=your_key_here
